\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/G\\u00e9rald_Darmanin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"104,000 spectators\", \"from\": 206, \"to\": 224}, {\"ngram\": \"the audacious, open-air event\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 257}, {\"ngram\": \"a floating parade\", \"from\": 289, \"to\": 306}, {\"ngram\": \"the Seine River\", \"from\": 310, \"to\": 325}, {\"ngram\": \"ticket holders\", \"from\": 343, \"to\": 357}, {\"ngram\": \"the lower riverbanks\", \"from\": 364, \"to\": 384}, {\"ngram\": \"another 222,000 spectators\", \"from\": 391, \"to\": 417}, {\"ngram\": \"the upper banks\", \"from\": 421, \"to\": 436}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple reports\", \"from\": 469, \"to\": 485}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement However, the free tickets will not be available to the general public, and will instead be invitation-only.\", \"from\": 488, \"to\": 610, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the free tickets\", \"from\": 511, \"to\": 527}, {\"ngram\": \"the general public\", \"from\": 553, \"to\": 571}, {\"ngram\": \"invitation\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To manage crowd movement, we can not tell everyone to come,\\\"Darmanin said, according to the Associated Press.\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 724, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 707, \"end\": 723, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.999998382614138, \"rank\": 1.617388568815372e-06, \"text\": \"Associated Press\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"crowd movement\", \"from\": 625, \"to\": 639}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 657, \"to\": 665}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For security reasons that everyone understands, notably the terrorist threat of recent weeks, we are obliged to make it free but contained.\\\"\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 866, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"security reasons\", \"from\": 730, \"to\": 746}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 752, \"to\": 760}, {\"ngram\": \"notably the terrorist threat\", \"from\": 774, \"to\": 802}, {\"ngram\": \"recent weeks\", \"from\": 806, \"to\": 818}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Two Interior Ministry officials said that ceremony access will be allotted with quotas to select residents of towns or regions hosting Olympic events, local sports federations and others chosen by event organizers or their partners, per the AP.\", \"from\": 868, \"to\": 1112, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 872, \"end\": 889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"score\": 0.9814579879575442, \"rank\": 0.018892313547929588, \"text\": \"Interior Ministry\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\"}, {\"begin\": 1109, \"end\": 1111, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 5.321126607062022e-12, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"ceremony access\", \"from\": 910, \"to\": 925}, {\"ngram\": \"quotas\", \"from\": 948, \"to\": 954}, {\"ngram\": \"residents\", \"from\": 965, \"to\": 974}, {\"ngram\": \"towns\", \"from\": 978, \"to\": 983}, {\"ngram\": \"regions\", \"from\": 987, \"to\": 994}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic events\", \"from\": 1003, \"to\": 1017}, {\"ngram\": \"local sports federations\", \"from\": 1019, \"to\": 1043}, {\"ngram\": \"others\", \"from\": 1048, \"to\": 1054}, {\"ngram\": \"event organizers\", \"from\": 1065, \"to\": 1081}, {\"ngram\": \"their partners\", \"from\": 1085, \"to\": 1099}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tourists will not be able to sign up for the free tickets, but an Interior Ministry official told the AP that the sports federations could invite foreign visitors as part of their quotas.\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1301, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1180, \"end\": 1197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"score\": 0.9814579879575442, \"rank\": 0.018892313547929588, \"text\": \"Interior Ministry\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q327333\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Federal_Ministry_of_the_Interior_and_Community\"}, {\"begin\": 1216, \"end\": 1218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 5.321126607062022e-12, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Tourists\", \"from\": 1114, \"to\": 1122}, {\"ngram\": \"the free tickets\", \"from\": 1155, \"to\": 1171}, {\"ngram\": \"the sports federations\", \"from\": 1224, \"to\": 1246}, {\"ngram\": \"foreign visitors\", \"from\": 1260, \"to\": 1276}, {\"ngram\": \"part\", \"from\": 1280, \"to\": 1284}, {\"ngram\": \"their quotas\", \"from\": 1288, \"to\": 1300}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The report also said that invited spectators will have to undergo security checks and will receive QR codes to get through security.\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1434, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The report\", \"from\": 1302, \"to\": 1312}, {\"ngram\": \"invited spectators\", \"from\": 1328, \"to\": 1346}, {\"ngram\": \"security checks\", \"from\": 1368, \"to\": 1383}, {\"ngram\": \"QR codes\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1409}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1433}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Organizers originally quoted the event as hosting 600,000 spectators, but Darmanin said earlier this year it would be about half that size, per reports.\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1588, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Organizers\", \"from\": 1436, \"to\": 1446}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1465, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"600,000 spectators\", \"from\": 1486, \"to\": 1504}, {\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 1510, \"to\": 1518}, {\"ngram\": \"about half that size\", \"from\": 1554, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"reports\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1587}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In another shift leading up to the Games and after pushback from local booksellers, a longtime fixture along the river, French President Emmanuel Macroncanceled plansto move their stands in preparation for the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 1589, \"to\": 1816, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1709, \"end\": 1725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French President\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/President_of_France\"}, {\"begin\": 1726, \"end\": 1734, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"score\": 0.9999996331549246, \"rank\": 3.431554680887538e-07, \"text\": \"Emmanuel\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Immanuel\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"another shift\", \"from\": 1592, \"to\": 1605}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 1620, \"to\": 1629}, {\"ngram\": \"pushback\", \"from\": 1640, \"to\": 1648}, {\"ngram\": \"local booksellers\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1671}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 1698, \"to\": 1707}, {\"ngram\": \"their stands\", \"from\": 1763, \"to\": 1775}, {\"ngram\": \"preparation\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1790}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening ceremony\", \"from\": 1795, \"to\": 1815}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Darmanin did not cite a specific security threat against the event, but said there are multiple potential threats, including those from Islamic extremist groups, violent environmental activists, far-right groups and cyberattacks from Russia or other adversaries, according to the AP.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 2101, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1954, \"end\": 1978, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Islamic extremist groups\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Islamic_extremism\"}, {\"begin\": 2052, \"end\": 2058, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.9999999930582817, \"rank\": 6.788304921622323e-09, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 2098, \"end\": 2100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999999895408, \"rank\": 5.321126607062022e-12, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Darmanin\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1826}, {\"ngram\": \"a specific security threat\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1866}, {\"ngram\": \"the event\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1884}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple potential threats\", \"from\": 1905, \"to\": 1931}, {\"ngram\": \"violent environmental activists\", \"from\": 1980, \"to\": 2011}, {\"ngram\": \"far-right groups\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2029}, {\"ngram\": \"cyberattacks\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2046}, {\"ngram\": \"other adversaries\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2079}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In January, Paris organizers said there would be roughly 2,000 private security guards in the seating venues closest to the river and about 45,000 security forces on the outer perimeter - 15 times the number of Paris police normally deployed for the entire Paris historical district.\", \"from\": 2103, \"to\": 2386, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2115, \"end\": 2120, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.396735305148315e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2314, \"end\": 2319, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.396735305148315e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2360, \"end\": 2365, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.396735305148315e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"January\", \"from\": 2106, \"to\": 2113}, {\"ngram\": \"roughly 2,000 private security guards\", \"from\": 2152, \"to\": 2189}, {\"ngram\": \"the seating venues\", \"from\": 2193, \"to\": 2211}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 2223, \"to\": 2232}, {\"ngram\": \"about 45,000 security forces\", \"from\": 2237, \"to\": 2265}, {\"ngram\": \"the outer perimeter\", \"from\": 2269, \"to\": 2288}, {\"ngram\": \"15 times the number\", \"from\": 2291, \"to\": 2310}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Advertisement At the time, Lambis Konstantinidis, director of planning and coordination for the Paris Games and a veteran of multiple Olympic organizing efforts, also said that contingency plans, for security or other concerns, were focused on \\\"having the ceremony on the river Seine\\\" rather than potentially moving the ceremony to a more traditional setting, like a stadium.\", \"from\": 2388, \"to\": 2764, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2405, \"to\": 2413}, {\"ngram\": \"Lambis Konstantinidis\", \"from\": 2415, \"to\": 2436}, {\"ngram\": \"director\", \"from\": 2438, \"to\": 2446}, {\"ngram\": \"planning\", \"from\": 2450, \"to\": 2458}, {\"ngram\": \"coordination\", \"from\": 2463, \"to\": 2475}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Games\", \"from\": 2480, \"to\": 2495}, {\"ngram\": \"a veteran\", \"from\": 2500, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"multiple Olympic organizing efforts\", \"from\": 2513, \"to\": 2548}, {\"ngram\": \"contingency plans\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2582}, {\"ngram\": \"security\", \"from\": 2588, \"to\": 2596}, {\"ngram\": \"other concerns\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2614}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2640, \"to\": 2652}, {\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 2656, \"to\": 2671}, {\"ngram\": \"the ceremony\", \"from\": 2704, \"to\": 2716}, {\"ngram\": \"a more traditional setting\", \"from\": 2720, \"to\": 2746}, {\"ngram\": \"a stadium\", \"from\": 2753, \"to\": 2762}]}, {\"sentence\": \"French security experts previously raised doubts about securing the banks of the Seine, and in December, Macron said there was \\\"obviously a Plan B, a Plan C\\\" in the face of elevated security risks.\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2963, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2766, \"end\": 2772, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"score\": 0.9527399147030168, \"rank\": 0.03292968691594247, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_language\"}, {\"begin\": 2847, \"end\": 2852, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 1.9108329422536744e-12, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2871, \"end\": 2877, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.4600978958693015e-20, \"text\": \"Macron\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emmanuel_Macron\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"doubts\", \"from\": 2808, \"to\": 2814}, {\"ngram\": \"the banks\", \"from\": 2830, \"to\": 2839}, {\"ngram\": \"December\", \"from\": 2861, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"obviously a Plan B\", \"from\": 2894, \"to\": 2912}, {\"ngram\": \"a Plan C\", \"from\": 2914, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"the face\", \"from\": 2927, \"to\": 2935}, {\"ngram\": \"elevated security risks\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2962}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"For us to come out and make this sort of bold commitment, we had a significant reassurance from the authorities that (securing an on-river opening ceremony) was feasible,\\\" Konstantinidis previously said.\", \"from\": 2965, \"to\": 3169, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2972}, {\"ngram\": \"this sort\", \"from\": 2994, \"to\": 3003}, {\"ngram\": \"bold commitment\", \"from\": 3007, \"to\": 3022}, {\"ngram\": \"a significant reassurance\", \"from\": 3031, \"to\": 3056}, {\"ngram\": \"the authorities\", \"from\": 3062, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"river\", \"from\": 3099, \"to\": 3104}, {\"ngram\": \"Konstantinidis\", \"from\": 3138, \"to\": 3152}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It requires means, it requires investment, but what the President said - we are already doing.\", \"from\": 3170, \"to\": 3265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"means\", \"from\": 3183, \"to\": 3188}, {\"ngram\": \"investment\", \"from\": 3202, \"to\": 3212}, {\"ngram\": \"the President\", \"from\": 3223, \"to\": 3236}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We have to have a contingency plan, but we need to have one anyway for a number of reasons that are not all security-related.\", \"from\": 3267, \"to\": 3393, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a contingency plan\", \"from\": 3284, \"to\": 3302}, {\"ngram\": \"a number\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3347}, {\"ngram\": \"reasons\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3358}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u2026 It's not about having it at the river Seine or in the stadium or (somewhere) else, but, could it look different?\\\"\", \"from\": 3394, \"to\": 3509, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the river Seine\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3439}, {\"ngram\": \"the stadium\", \"from\": 3446, \"to\": 3457}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The opening ceremony is slated to take place July 26 with the floating parade along the river featuring a 3.7-mile journey in which delegations from 200 countries will board 100 boats for a 45-minute ride that begins near the national library, winds past the Cathedral of Notre Dame and the Louvre, passes by all of Paris' famous centrally located gardens and ends at the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3802, \"end\": 3808, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre_Palace\", \"score\": 0.9132464835749832, \"rank\": 0.09499463505758603, \"text\": \"Louvre\", \"types\": [\"Q41176\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre_Palace\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Louvre_Palace\"}, {\"begin\": 3827, \"end\": 3832, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.396735305148315e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The opening ceremony\", \"from\": 3511, \"to\": 3531}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 3550, \"to\": 3555}, {\"ngram\": \"the floating parade\", \"from\": 3569, \"to\": 3588}, {\"ngram\": \"the river\", \"from\": 3595, \"to\": 3604}, {\"ngram\": \"a 3.7-mile journey\", \